## Limitations

The findings are based on available online resources and may not encompass all perspectives on strategic management. The data is limited to the information provided by the sources accessed, and there may be additional insights in academic journals or proprietary industry reports not included in this analysis. Additionally, the dynamic nature of strategic management means that practices and emphases can evolve, potentially affecting the relevance of the findings over time.